The error in the program is because the record does not have a 'points' att
attribute. The correct attribute name should be 'score'. Here is the correc
corrected version of your Tundra code:

```tundra
val report = {
  user: {
    name: "Ada",
    score: 10
  },
  bonus: 2
};

val total = report.user.score + report.bonus;
print(total);
```
